create table customer (
        active boolean not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        address TEXT,
        mobile varchar(255) not null unique,
        name varchar(255) not null,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table customer_cylinder_ledger (
        transaction_date date not null,
        balance bigint not null,
        customer_id bigint not null,
        empty_in bigint not null,
        filled_out bigint not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        ref_id bigint not null,
        variant_id bigint not null,
        ref_type varchar(255) not null check (ref_type in ('SALE','EMPTY_RETURN')),
        primary key (id)
    )

create table cylinder_variant (
        active boolean not null,
        weight_kg float(53) not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        name varchar(255) not null unique,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table inventory_stock (
        empty_qty bigint not null,
        filled_qty bigint not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        last_updated timestamp(6) not null,
        variant_id bigint not null,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table monthly_price (
        base_price numeric(38,2) not null,
        created_at date not null,
        month_year date not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        variant_id bigint not null,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table sale (
        sale_date date not null,
        total_amount numeric(38,2) not null,
        created_at timestamp(6) not null,
        customer_id bigint not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table sale_item (
        base_price numeric(38,2) not null,
        discount numeric(38,2) not null,
        final_price numeric(38,2) not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        qty_empty_received bigint not null,
        qty_issued bigint not null,
        sale_id bigint not null,
        variant_id bigint not null,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table supplier (
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        contact varchar(255) not null,
        name varchar(255) not null,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table supplier_transaction (
        transaction_date date not null,
        empty_sent bigint not null,
        filled_received bigint not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        supplier_id bigint not null,
        variant_id bigint not null,
        reference TEXT,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table customer (
        active boolean not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        address TEXT,
        mobile varchar(255) not null unique,
        name varchar(255) not null,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table customer_cylinder_ledger (
        transaction_date date not null,
        balance bigint not null,
        customer_id bigint not null,
        empty_in bigint not null,
        filled_out bigint not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        ref_id bigint not null,
        variant_id bigint not null,
        ref_type varchar(255) not null check (ref_type in ('SALE','EMPTY_RETURN')),
        primary key (id)
    )

create table cylinder_variant (
        active boolean not null,
        weight_kg float(53) not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        name varchar(255) not null unique,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table inventory_stock (
        empty_qty bigint not null,
        filled_qty bigint not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        last_updated timestamp(6) not null,
        variant_id bigint not null,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table monthly_price (
        base_price numeric(38,2) not null,
        created_at date not null,
        month_year date not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        variant_id bigint not null,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table sale (
        sale_date date not null,
        total_amount numeric(38,2) not null,
        created_at timestamp(6) not null,
        customer_id bigint not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table sale_item (
        base_price numeric(38,2) not null,
        discount numeric(38,2) not null,
        final_price numeric(38,2) not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        qty_empty_received bigint not null,
        qty_issued bigint not null,
        sale_id bigint not null,
        variant_id bigint not null,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table supplier (
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        contact varchar(255) not null,
        name varchar(255) not null,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table supplier_transaction (
        transaction_date date not null,
        empty_sent bigint not null,
        filled_received bigint not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        supplier_id bigint not null,
        variant_id bigint not null,
        reference TEXT,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table customer (
        active boolean not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        address TEXT,
        mobile varchar(255) not null unique,
        name varchar(255) not null,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table customer_cylinder_ledger (
        transaction_date date not null,
        balance bigint not null,
        customer_id bigint not null,
        empty_in bigint not null,
        filled_out bigint not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        ref_id bigint not null,
        variant_id bigint not null,
        ref_type varchar(255) not null check (ref_type in ('SALE','EMPTY_RETURN')),
        primary key (id)
    )

create table cylinder_variant (
        active boolean not null,
        weight_kg float(53) not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        name varchar(255) not null unique,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table inventory_stock (
        empty_qty bigint not null,
        filled_qty bigint not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        last_updated timestamp(6) not null,
        variant_id bigint not null,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table monthly_price (
        base_price numeric(38,2) not null,
        created_at date not null,
        month_year date not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        variant_id bigint not null,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table sale (
        sale_date date not null,
        total_amount numeric(38,2) not null,
        created_at timestamp(6) not null,
        customer_id bigint not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table sale_item (
        base_price numeric(38,2) not null,
        discount numeric(38,2) not null,
        final_price numeric(38,2) not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        qty_empty_received bigint not null,
        qty_issued bigint not null,
        sale_id bigint not null,
        variant_id bigint not null,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table supplier (
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        contact varchar(255) not null,
        name varchar(255) not null,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table supplier_transaction (
        transaction_date date not null,
        empty_sent bigint not null,
        filled_received bigint not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        supplier_id bigint not null,
        variant_id bigint not null,
        reference TEXT,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table customer (
        active boolean not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        address TEXT,
        mobile varchar(255) not null unique,
        name varchar(255) not null,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table customer_cylinder_ledger (
        transaction_date date not null,
        balance bigint not null,
        customer_id bigint not null,
        empty_in bigint not null,
        filled_out bigint not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        ref_id bigint not null,
        variant_id bigint not null,
        ref_type varchar(255) not null check (ref_type in ('SALE','EMPTY_RETURN')),
        primary key (id)
    )

create table cylinder_variant (
        active boolean not null,
        weight_kg float(53) not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        name varchar(255) not null unique,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table inventory_stock (
        empty_qty bigint not null,
        filled_qty bigint not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        last_updated timestamp(6) not null,
        variant_id bigint not null,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table monthly_price (
        base_price numeric(38,2) not null,
        created_at date not null,
        month_year date not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        variant_id bigint not null,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table sale (
        sale_date date not null,
        total_amount numeric(38,2) not null,
        created_at timestamp(6) not null,
        customer_id bigint not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table sale_item (
        base_price numeric(38,2) not null,
        discount numeric(38,2) not null,
        final_price numeric(38,2) not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        qty_empty_received bigint not null,
        qty_issued bigint not null,
        sale_id bigint not null,
        variant_id bigint not null,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table supplier (
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        contact varchar(255) not null,
        name varchar(255) not null,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table supplier_transaction (
        transaction_date date not null,
        empty_sent bigint not null,
        filled_received bigint not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        supplier_id bigint not null,
        variant_id bigint not null,
        reference TEXT,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table customer (
        active boolean not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        address TEXT,
        mobile varchar(255) not null unique,
        name varchar(255) not null,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table customer_cylinder_ledger (
        transaction_date date not null,
        balance bigint not null,
        customer_id bigint not null,
        empty_in bigint not null,
        filled_out bigint not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        ref_id bigint not null,
        variant_id bigint not null,
        ref_type varchar(255) not null check (ref_type in ('SALE','EMPTY_RETURN')),
        primary key (id)
    )

create table cylinder_variant (
        active boolean not null,
        weight_kg float(53) not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        name varchar(255) not null unique,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table inventory_stock (
        empty_qty bigint not null,
        filled_qty bigint not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        last_updated timestamp(6) not null,
        variant_id bigint not null,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table monthly_price (
        base_price numeric(38,2) not null,
        created_at date not null,
        month_year date not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        variant_id bigint not null,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table sale (
        sale_date date not null,
        total_amount numeric(38,2) not null,
        created_at timestamp(6) not null,
        customer_id bigint not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table sale_item (
        base_price numeric(38,2) not null,
        discount numeric(38,2) not null,
        final_price numeric(38,2) not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        qty_empty_received bigint not null,
        qty_issued bigint not null,
        sale_id bigint not null,
        variant_id bigint not null,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table supplier (
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        contact varchar(255) not null,
        name varchar(255) not null,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table supplier_transaction (
        transaction_date date not null,
        empty_sent bigint not null,
        filled_received bigint not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        supplier_id bigint not null,
        variant_id bigint not null,
        reference TEXT,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table customer (
        active boolean not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        address TEXT,
        mobile varchar(255) not null unique,
        name varchar(255) not null,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table customer_cylinder_ledger (
        transaction_date date not null,
        balance bigint not null,
        customer_id bigint not null,
        empty_in bigint not null,
        filled_out bigint not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        ref_id bigint not null,
        variant_id bigint not null,
        ref_type varchar(255) not null check (ref_type in ('SALE','EMPTY_RETURN')),
        primary key (id)
    )

create table cylinder_variant (
        active boolean not null,
        weight_kg float(53) not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        name varchar(255) not null unique,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table inventory_stock (
        empty_qty bigint not null,
        filled_qty bigint not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        last_updated timestamp(6) not null,
        variant_id bigint not null,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table monthly_price (
        base_price numeric(38,2) not null,
        created_at date not null,
        month_year date not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        variant_id bigint not null,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table sale (
        sale_date date not null,
        total_amount numeric(38,2) not null,
        created_at timestamp(6) not null,
        customer_id bigint not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table sale_item (
        base_price numeric(38,2) not null,
        discount numeric(38,2) not null,
        final_price numeric(38,2) not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        qty_empty_received bigint not null,
        qty_issued bigint not null,
        sale_id bigint not null,
        variant_id bigint not null,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table supplier (
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        contact varchar(255) not null,
        name varchar(255) not null,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table supplier_transaction (
        transaction_date date not null,
        empty_sent bigint not null,
        filled_received bigint not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        supplier_id bigint not null,
        variant_id bigint not null,
        reference TEXT,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table customer (
        active boolean not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        address TEXT,
        mobile varchar(255) not null unique,
        name varchar(255) not null,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table customer_cylinder_ledger (
        transaction_date date not null,
        balance bigint not null,
        customer_id bigint not null,
        empty_in bigint not null,
        filled_out bigint not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        ref_id bigint not null,
        variant_id bigint not null,
        ref_type varchar(255) not null check (ref_type in ('SALE','EMPTY_RETURN')),
        primary key (id)
    )

create table cylinder_variant (
        active boolean not null,
        weight_kg float(53) not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        name varchar(255) not null unique,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table inventory_stock (
        empty_qty bigint not null,
        filled_qty bigint not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        last_updated timestamp(6) not null,
        variant_id bigint not null,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table monthly_price (
        base_price numeric(38,2) not null,
        created_at date not null,
        month_year date not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        variant_id bigint not null,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table sale (
        sale_date date not null,
        total_amount numeric(38,2) not null,
        created_at timestamp(6) not null,
        customer_id bigint not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table sale_item (
        base_price numeric(38,2) not null,
        discount numeric(38,2) not null,
        final_price numeric(38,2) not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        qty_empty_received bigint not null,
        qty_issued bigint not null,
        sale_id bigint not null,
        variant_id bigint not null,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table supplier (
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        contact varchar(255) not null,
        name varchar(255) not null,
        primary key (id)
    )

create table supplier_transaction (
        transaction_date date not null,
        empty_sent bigint not null,
        filled_received bigint not null,
        id bigint generated by default as identity,
        supplier_id bigint not null,
        variant_id bigint not null,
        reference TEXT,
        primary key (id)
    )
